Russian TV crews just happen to be around when the Ukrainians (ie Russians) blew up a rebel leaders car.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/37G3dqJ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>The car in question. You may be thinking that that is a very cheap looking car for the leader of a Russian backed rebel to drive.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/C6rkFjW.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>And you would be right. This is the actual expensive UAZ Patriot he drives.

They took the license plate off of the actual car and put it on a cheap old UAZ to blow up instead. Seriously.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/rZyZRP6.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>False flag attack on occupied Donbass Vasylivka water pumping station. 

A Russia TV crew just happened to be at the pump when shelling started.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/bcCKXJO.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Russian TV crew just happens to in the area of a false flag attack. This same crew just happened to be at the location the car bombing earlier.

Weird how the Ukrainians only attack areas right next to Russian TV crews.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/BXKGl5q.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>False flag attack.

Occupation authorities in parts of Donetsk region claim that they’ve killed two members of saboteur group of Ukrainian army attempting to blow up cylinders with chlorine in Horlivka. This is a lie.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/zN535TT.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Russian sources claim the video of the false flag attack came from both the dead saboteurs as well as rebel militia. Getting a story consistent is hard.

Not going to bother posting the video as it is 1: Russia misinformation, and 2: It is just some dudes shooting in the woods with obvious audio overlay of prerecorded radio traffic.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/qgIKje2.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Metadata shows the video of the rebel leaders speech about the false flag attacks was recorded before said attacks took place.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/rDHE6Cg.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>After being loaded on buses in Russian controlled rebel regions as part of a staged evacuation civilians are abandoned by Russia. Refugees sit on buses for several hours without food and the opportunity to go to the toilet, complain about the cold, worsening health problems and ask for help. Buses stand with the ignition off, the interior is not heated</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/EYEBB2J.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>What Russia claims is the Ukrainian plan to attack the Russian controlled Donbass region. It is a fake.

The plan is written in Russian, not Ukrainian, and uses Russian place names rather then Ukrainian. An obvious fake for domestic consumption.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/HjxzPFZ.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Anti-aircraft fire over Donetsk tonight.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/IdV7Jif.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>In a shocking turn of events Boris Johnson has good ideas.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/SNIsDX4.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Ukrainian President Zelensky says that if Ukraine doesn’t receive new security guarantees from the Budapest Memorandum signatories, all articles of the 1994 agreement may be considered void.

In the agreement Ukraine gave up its nuclear arsenal for security guarantees.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/IKpSXhu.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>The 11 MHz HF Aero-OR subband in Europe. 

The Russian military has turned the volume on their OTH-B radar to max, that is wartime frequency and power, in an attempt to track stealth aircraft & drones.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/uUWA213.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Russian armor near the border now has tactical markings applied.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/zW9P4aM.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Russian artillery on the move 7km from the Ukrainian border. Source claims at least 31 guns.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/JGbDfbv.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Belarus becomes an occupied state. 

Putin has been pushing for a "union state" of Belarus and Russia for months now. Lukashenko has repeatedly prostrated to Putin, including stating his Army will follow orders from Moscow, due to his weak position and this appears to be the final act.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/5qjv6dq.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Kremlin propaganda mouthpiece Russia Today claims Ukraine has shelled Russia. This claim is false.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/cfFgsGh.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Last minute aid from the Dutch. Not much but every little bit of democratic solidarity matters.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/o3qNoKa.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Canadian arms land in Ukraine. Canada had previously declined to send weapons but has reversed that decision.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/PCOiKxR.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Estonia delivers Javelin anti-tank missiles to Ukraine.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/YUIwXZ1.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>The missiles.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/6FB2E5g.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Ukrainian Militia on exercise.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/cGnCdD1.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Many militia courses are taught by foreign volunteers, largely US, UK and Georgian vets.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/OYPiCuX.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Raw recruits are given wooden guns to learn firearm basics on.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/W6zUh1R.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>The Ukrainian Army announces the first combat death of the current crisis, cause was Russian shelling.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/5xUXK8D.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Cat tax.

Reject misinformation and stay informed. This was a long post today with little movement on the diplomatic front. Hopefully that will change. 

Stay safe out there.

РАЗОМ ПЕРЕМОЖЕМО!</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/M1t8ia1</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[RedE100]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>#</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/U4RKJai</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/FDitCY8.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/U4RKJai</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[mfrybeasley]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>So wholesome</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/VjBO9IB</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/c8xYBMD.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/VjBO9IB</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[GorgeousGeorgieous]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>What we know</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/CrcmC9x</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/0EiEkTu.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/CrcmC9x</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[mfrybeasley]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Stop Motion Magic</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/72og1mv</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Dm8X1H9.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>From Coraline</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/72og1mv</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[mfrybeasley]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>They accidentally awarded the gold medal to 3rd place so she in turn awarded it to 1st place herself.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/zknbyCJ</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/3EVLPfN.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/zknbyCJ</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Sarahmissa1]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Dead Ringers Redux</title>